How to run this project.


1. To Download this project.
  a.Click the "Fork" button.
  b.Execute the following commands
      git clone git@github.com:lukshica/yschool-mini-lukshica-ass4-JPA.git
  
2. Create a database studentdetails
  a.Start mysql server
  b.create a database named studentdetails 

3. Run the project.
  a.Open commands prompt and navigate the project folder which has the pom.xml
  b.run the following commands to run the project.
      mvn compile
      mvn jetty:run 
4.Then go to the browser and type below address
  a.http://localhost:8080/yschool-mini-lukshica-ass4-JPA